---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
---

<Page
	title="About"
	description="About Shuguang Zhang, his research focus, background, collaboration interests, and personal disclaimer."
>
	<section class="intro">
		<p class="eyebrow">About</p>
		<h1>Research-oriented engineering at the edge of AI, cryptography, and finance</h1>
		<p>
			我关注金融基础设施中的 AI 安全、密码工程、隐私计算与智能体治理，尤其是能够落到系统、工具和可审计流程里的研究问题。
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section split" aria-labelledby="who-title">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Who I am</p>
			<h2 id="who-title">张曙光 / Shuguang Zhang</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="statement">
			<p>
				我的核心兴趣是把密码与隐私计算、AI Agent 安全、金融科技安全实践放在同一个问题空间里：当 AI 系统开始连接知识库、工具、记忆和真实业务流程时，安全边界应该如何被重新设计。
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" aria-labelledby="work-title">
		<div class="section-header">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">What I work on</p>
				<h2 id="work-title">Systems, not slogans</h2>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="two-column-grid">
			<article class="card">
				<h3>AI Security and Agent Governance</h3>
				<p>Agent memory, tool-use security, action audit, multi-tenant isolation, and enterprise AI safety controls.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Cryptographic Engineering</h3>
				<p>Post-quantum migration, cryptographic asset discovery, privacy-preserving computation, and implementation practice.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Secure RAG and Financial Knowledge</h3>
				<p>Least-privilege retrieval, sensitive data minimization, secure ranking, and auditable generation workflows.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="card">
				<h3>Research Practice</h3>
				<p>Turning paper ideas into prototypes, notes, experiments, manuscripts, and reusable engineering knowledge.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section split" aria-labelledby="background-title">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Background</p>
			<h2 id="background-title">Crypto, privacy computing, and financial security practice</h2>
		</div>
		<div>
			<p>
				背景覆盖密码与隐私计算研究、金融科技安全实践，以及面向企业落地的 AI 安全系统设计。本站会优先公开不涉及单位内部信息的研究想法、工程方法和个人技术观点。
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section split" aria-labelledby="collab-title">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Collaboration</p>
			<h2 id="collab-title">Topics I am open to explore</h2>
		</div>
		<div>
			<p>
				欢迎围绕金融 AI 安全、Agent 安全、PQC 迁移、Secure RAG、隐私计算系统开展研究合作，尤其是能够结合真实约束、可运行系统和论文表达的问题。
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section" aria-labelledby="disclaimer-title">
		<div class="disclaimer">
			<p class="eyebrow">Disclaimer</p>
			<h2 id="disclaimer-title">Personal views only</h2>
			<p>本文和本站内容仅代表个人研究与技术观点，不代表所在单位立场。</p>
			<p>The views expressed here are my own and do not represent my employer.</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Page>
